desc: Fiber Artist, Audrian Manfull has designed Art and Gifts to fit any Room in your life, since 1989. Freestyle designs for Modern, Gothic and Cottage, lifestyles. Holiday and everyday wares - including one-of-a-kind items to Special Event Gifts utilizing new, discarded and upcycled materials. Over 45 years of creating.

layout.text: Treat yourself to some simple, pleasures.
